  "desc": "Beautifully maintained 2-bed, 2.5-bath end-unit in Holmdel Mews. Wood-burning fireplace, finished basement, eat-in kitchen with pantry and slider to patio. Low-maintenance living in one of Holmdel's most desirable communities.",
  "description": "This beautifully maintained end-unit townhouse offers the perfect blend of privacy, space, and low-maintenance living in one of Holmdel's most desirable communities. With approximately 1,778 sq ft, this 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is thoughtfully designed for both everyday comfort and easy entertaining.\n\nStep inside to a welcoming foyer with ceramic tile flooring that leads into a bright and spacious living room featuring a wood-burning fireplace — perfect for cozy evenings. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with ample cabinetry, pantry storage, and a sliding glass door that opens to your outdoor space, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor flow.\n\nUpstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite with a full bath, offering a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The finished basement adds valuable bonus space — ideal for a home office, gym, media room, or guest area.",
